Looking at the baseline and target screenshots, I can identify the key visual differences:

1. **Baseline** shows inputs with labels ("标签文字") on the left side, with the label and input on the same row (horizontal layout)
2. **Target** shows inputs without labels, appearing as full-width input boxes with centered placeholder text
3. The target is missing the label display in the basic input rows, and the overall layout structure differs significantly

The main issues in the target:
- Input items don't show labels inline (the label appears but the layout seems off)
- The target renders inputs as bordered boxes rather than the clean list-style with bottom borders
- Placeholder text appears centered in target but should be left-aligned after the label
- The overall padding and spacing differs

Let me analyze the diff image more carefully - the red areas show significant differences in the label area and input positioning. The target seems to be rendering without proper horizontal label+input layout, and has extra border styling that shouldn't be there.

<<<FILE path="t-input.theme.less">>>
/**
 * Input 样式（与 @tdesign/uniapp 视觉对齐：列表内嵌型、下分割线、状态色）
 * 全部颜色 / 间距走 CSS Variables，命名沿用 --td-input-* 系列。
 */

// ------- 默认 token -------
@td-input-vertical-padding: var(--td-input-vertical-padding, 16px);
@td-input-horizontal-padding: var(--td-input-horizontal-padding, 16px);

@td-input-bg-color: var(--td-input-bg-color, #ffffff);
@td-input-text-color: var(--td-input-default-text-color, #181818);
@td-input-disabled-text-color: var(--td-input-disabled-text-color, #c0c0c0);
@td-input-placeholder-text-color: var(--td-input-placeholder-text-color, #c0c0c0);

@td-input-label-color: var(--td-input-label-text-color, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9));
@td-input-suffix-text-color: var(--td-input-suffix-text-color, #181818);
@td-input-suffix-icon-color: var(--td-input-suffix-icon-color, #c0c0c0);
@td-input-prefix-icon-color: var(--td-input-prefix-icon-color, #181818);

@td-input-border-color: var(--td-input-border-color, #e7e7e7);
@td-input-border-left-space: var(--td-input-border-left-space, 16px);
@td-input-border-right-space: var(--td-input-border-right-space, 0);
@td-input-align-items: var(--td-input-align-items, center);

@td-input-success-color: var(--td-input-success-tips-color, #2ba471);
@td-input-warning-color: var(--td-input-warning-tips-color, #ed7b2f);
@td-input-error-color: var(--td-input-error-tips-color, #d54941);

@td-input-label-min-width: var(--td-input-label-min-width, 32px);
@td-input-label-max-width: var(--td-input-label-max-width, 80px);

.t-input {
  display: flex;
  align-items: @td-input-align-items;
  flex-direction: row;
  flex: 1;
  width: 100%;
  padding: @td-input-vertical-padding @td-input-horizontal-padding;
  background-color: @td-input-bg-color;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;

  // ---- 下分割线（borderless=false 时） ----
  &--border::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: @td-input-border-left-space;
    right: @td-input-border-right-space;
    bottom: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background-color: @td-input-border-color;
    transform: scaleY(0.5);
    transform-origin: 0 100%;
  }

  // ---- 竖排 ----
  &--layout-vertical {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  // ---- prefix 区（icon + label） ----
  &__wrap--prefix {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-right: 16px;
  }

  &__icon--prefix {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: @td-input-prefix-icon-color;
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-right: 4px;

    &:empty {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  &__label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: @td-input-label-color;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 24px;
    word-wrap: break-word;

    &:empty {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  &__label-text {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: @td-input-label-color;
    line-height: 24px;
  }

  &--layout-vertical &__wrap--prefix {
    margin-right: 0;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  &--layout-vertical &__label {
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-right: 0;
  }

  &--layout-vertical &__label-text {
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  // ---- 内容主体 wrap ----
  &__wrap {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    flex: 1;
    flex-shrink: 1;
    min-width: 0;
    width: 100%;
  }

  &__content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 24px;
  }

  // ---- input 控件 ----
  &__control {
    flex: 1;
    display: block;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    width: 100%;
    min-width: 0;
    min-height: 24px;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    border: 0;
    background: transparent;
    color: @td-input-text-color;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 24px;

    &--disabled {
      color: @td-input-disabled-text-color;
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }

    &--read-only {
      cursor: default;
    }
  }

  &__placeholder {
    color: @td-input-placeholder-text-color;
    font-size: 16px;

    &--disabled {
      color: @td-input-disabled-text-color;
    }
  }

  // ---- 文本对齐 ----
  &--left   { text-align: left; }
  &--center { text-align: center; }
  &--right  { text-align: right; }

  // ---- 后置区域 ----
  &__wrap--clearable-icon,
  &__wrap--suffix-icon,
  &__wrap--suffix {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    padding-left: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;

    &:empty {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  &__wrap--clearable-icon,
  &__wrap--suffix-icon {
    color: @td-input-suffix-icon-color;
    font-size: 24px;
  }

  &__wrap--suffix {
    color: @td-input-suffix-text-color;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  // 兜底的 ✕（无 t-icon 时使用）
  &__clear-fallback {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    line-height: 18px;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #c5c5c5;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  // ---- tips ----
  &__tips {
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 20px;
    padding-top: 4px;

    &.t-input--default { color: @td-input-placeholder-text-color; }
    &.t-input--success { color: @td-input-success-color; }
    &.t-input--warning { color: @td-input-warning-color; }
    &.t-input--error   { color: @td-input-error-color; }
  }

  &__tips-text {
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 20px;
  }

  // ---- 禁用 / 只读 ----
  &--disabled .t-input__control,
  &--readonly .t-input__control {
    color: @td-input-disabled-text-color;
  }
}
<<<END>>>
